text: Siret Räämet (born 31 December 1999) is an Estonian footballer who plays as a defender and has appeared for the Estonia women's national team. ==Career== Räämet has been capped for the Estonia national team, appearing for the team during the UEFA Women's Euro 2021 qualifying cycle. ==References== ==External links== * * * * Category:1999 births Category:Living people Category:Sportspeople from Tallinn Category:Estonian women's footballers Category:Estonia women's international footballers Category:Women's association football defenders
title: Siret Räämet
